s-splits-emerge-multiple-issues?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国向海南开放更多种类的免签旅游，力求将海南转变为主要自由贸易港</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251561/china-opens-hainan-more-kinds-visa-free-travel?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>某些护照持有者现在可以进入该岛长达 30 天，不仅可以旅游，还可以商务和家庭旅行。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 12:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251561/china-opens-hainan-more-kinds-visa-free-travel?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国的中产阶级是北京经济复苏计划的关键，由于对财富和收入的担忧，他们暂停了支出</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251554/chinas-middle-class-key-beijings-economic-recovery-plan-put-spending-hold-over-wealth-income?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>一项广泛用于衡量中国中产阶级健康状况的指标显示，去年第四季度家庭财富和收入指数仍处于收缩状态。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 10:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251554/chinas-middle-class-key-beijings-economic-recovery-plan-put-spending-hold-over-wealth-income?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国计划斥资10亿美元改造坦赞铁路，争夺控制关键矿产贸易路线</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251559/china-plans-spend-us1-billion-revamp-tanzania-zambia-railway-race-control-critical-mineral-trade?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>连接赞比亚铜矿带和达累斯萨拉姆港的坦赞铁路线将通过公私合作伙伴关系进行更新，并与美国和欧盟支持的资源丰富地区和安哥拉大西洋海岸之间的铁路线竞争。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 09:26:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251559/china-plans-spend-us1-billion-revamp-tanzania-zambia-railway-race-control-critical-mineral-trade?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国学术明星被解雇、香港梅西传奇、“哈佛女孩”重回聚光灯下：《南华早报》本周七大亮点</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3251476/chinas-academic-star-sacked-hong-kongs-messi-saga-harvard-girl-back-spotlight-scmps-7-highlights?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>从香港的梅西戏剧到中国的“哈佛女孩”重回聚光灯下，以下是《南华早报》近期报道的